http_set_scope.text: http_set_scope: Define in-scope host (and optionally subdomains) so out-of-scope requests are skipped.

http_repeater.text: http_repeater: Send a crafted request (Burp Repeater equivalent). request_spec keys: url, method, headers, cookies, data.

location: query|body|headers|cookie.
